\begin_layout Section
Scenarios
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In this section we decided to provide these scenarios for three of the most
 important feature of our website: user registration, user login and user
 cart management.
 All these feature have to deal with user authentication: for this reason
 we decided to analyze these scenarios.
\end_layout

